## Description {#details}

Analysis pass providing the <code><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/basicblocksectionsprofilereader">BasicBlockSectionsProfileReader</a></code>.

Note that this pass&#39;s result cannot be invalidated, it is immutable for the life of the module.
